A '''holosign''' was a sign that was represented by a [[Hologram/Legends|hologram]]. It would display usually static text or images, but had the capability of updating.

==History==
In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], a huge holosign was hanging in the air above Customs Central on [[Aargau/Legends|Aargau]] read "WELCOME TO AARGAU, JEWEL OF THE [[Zug system/Legends|ZUG SYSTEM]]! OBSERVE THE FOLLOWING [[Three Statutes of Aargau|RULES]]."

In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], a holosign hung ornately over the doors of the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building's]] [[Grand Convocation Chamber]] by [[Tolik Yar]] read "882 DAYS WITHOUT A SHOT BEING FIRED IN ANGER. Remember, Peace Is No Accident."

